highlights.text: “Soleil Bleu” by Bleu Soleil and LUIZA has been on Viral Songs France the longest, at 133 days straight.
La Rvfleuze has the most spots on Viral Songs France. “Serrure #5” is the highest at #15.
“Yuck (feat. Ken Carson)” by Young Thug and Ken Carson is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs France, up 10 spots at #65.
“NOW OR NEVER” by Tkandz and CXSPER is the highest new entry on Viral Songs France at #1.
